org.cyclops.cyclopscore.fluid

Class SingleUseTank

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraftforge.fluids.FluidTank
      • org.cyclops.cyclopscore.fluid.Tank
        • org.cyclops.cyclopscore.fluid.SingleUseTank
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.minecraftforge.fluids.capability.IFluidHandler, net.minecraftforge.fluids.IFluidTank

    public class SingleUseTank
extends Tank
    A simple tank that can accept and drain fluids until the capacity is reached. Only one fluid can be accepted, which must be specified with setAcceptedFluid(Fluid). Based on the Buildcraft SingleUseTank. Implement SingleUseTank.IUpdateListener on the given tile to make it listen to tank changes.
